snippet.title: Marvel Puzzle Quest: Dark Reign Trailer
snippet.description:
The villains have taken over in "Marvel Puzzle Quest: Dark Reign," now availabe on iOS and Android devices! Assemble a team of Marvel's biggest super heroes and villains and battle with Puzzle Quest's trademark match-3 and story-telling gameplay in a game that combines favorite Marvel characters with a deep RPG leveling, player vs. player, character upgrades, and more.

Download "Marvel Puzzle Quest: Dark Reign" on iOS devices: http://bit.ly/1hnUuNy
Download "Marvel Puzzle Quest: Dark Reign" on Android devices: http://bit.ly/15OeZOa
